title: WEDNESDAY 1/27 - QBs on the move
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY 1/27 - QBs on the move
description:
Aaron Rodgers future in Green Bay seemed a little murky following the loss to the Buccaneers, but Packers president Mark Murphy (0:23) and Rodgers himself (0:48) clearing the air on Tuesday. Jared Goff's (1:20) time in LA still unclear and GM Les Snead (1:39) not exactly giving the vote of confidence Goff wanted to hear. One QB we know will be on the move is Matthew Stafford (1:55). Former Lions legend Barry Sanders explains why (2:11). The Washington Football Team making history Tuesday (2:36) and the Senior Bowl is underway (2:55) in Mobile, Alabama
